            <p>In this <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-space_technology" target="_blank">Open Space</a> style conference, you will have a rare opportunity to contribute to and learn from conversations with people like <a href=
            "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kent_Beck" target="_blank">Kent Beck</a>. This is not a conference where you sit passively for long presentations.  It is a meeting of the minds to discuss the present and future of Agile Development.</p>
